quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  32,11,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Malayika w’urupfu ubashinzwe azabatwara ubuzima; hanyuma kwa Nyagasani wanyu ni ho muzasubizwa"
  32,12,"(Wari kubona bikomeye) iyaba wari kuzabona inkozi z’ibibi zubitse imitwe imbere ya Nyagasani wazo (zigira ziti) \"Nyagasani! Twabonye kandi twumvise (ukuri kw’ibyo twahakanaga). Bityo, dusubize (ku isi) dukore ibikorwa byiza. Mu by’ukuri, (ubu) twamenye ukuri"
  32,13,"N’iyo tuza kubishaka buri wese twari kumuha ukuyoboka kwe, ariko ijambo (ry’ibihano) rinturutseho ni impamo ko rwose nzuzuza umuriro wa Jahanamu amajini n’abantu bose hamwe"
  32,14,"Ngaho nimusogongere (ibihano) kubera kwibagirwa ko muzahura n’uyu munsi wanyu. Mu by’ukuri, natwe twabibagiwe; bityo nimusogongere ibihano bizahoraho kubera ibyo mwajyaga mukora"
  32,15,"Mu by’ukuri, abemera amagambo yacu, ni babandi igihe bayibukijwe bitura hasi bakubama, banasingiza ishimwe n’ikuzo bya Nyagasani wabo, kandi batibona"
  32,16,"Begura imbavu zabo muburyamo bwabo kugira ngo basabe Nyagasani wabo batinya (ibihano) kandi bizera (ingororano ze), ndetse bakanatanga mu byo twabafunguriye"
  32,17,"Nta n’umwe uzi ibyo bahishiwe bishimishije, bizaba ingororano z’ibyo bajyaga bakora"
  32,18,Ese uwemera (Allah) ni kimwe n’inkozi y’ibibi? Ntibashobora kureshya (imbere ya Allah)
  32,19,"Ariko babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazagororerwa ubuturo mu ijuru nk’izimano ry’ibyo bajyaga bakora"
  32,20,"Naho inkozi z’ibibi, ubuturo bwazo buzaba umuriro; buri uko bazajya bashaka kuwuvamo, bazajya bawusubizwamo maze babwirwe bati \"Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano by’umuriro mwajyaga muhakana"
  32,21,Kandi rwose tuzabasogongeza ku bihano byoroheje (bya hano ku isi) mbere y’ibihano bikomeye (byo ku mperuka) kugira ngo bisubireho
  32,22,"Ni na nde nkozi y’ibibi kurusha uwibutswa amagambo ya Nyagasani we maze akayatera umugongo? Mu by’ukuri, tuzahana inkozi z’ibibi"
  32,23,"Kandi rwose twahaye Musa igitabo (Tawurati). Bityo, ntuzagire ugushidikanya ko kuzahura na we 103. Kandi twakigize umuyoboro kuri bene Isiraheli"
  32,24,"Kandi bamwe muri bo (bene Isiraheli) twabagize abayobozi bayobora ku bw’itegeko ryacu, ubwo bihanganaga bakanemera amagambo yacu batayashidikanyaho"
  32,25,"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe ni we uzabakiranura ku munsi w’imperuka mu byo batavugagaho rumwe"
  32,26,"Ese ntibibabera ikimenyetso iyo bibajije umubare w’ibisekuru twarimbuye mbere yabo, bakaba banyura mu matongo yabyo? Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso; ese ntibumva"
  32,27,"Ese ntibabona uko twohereza amazi ku butaka bwumagaye, tukayeresha ibimera bitanga amafunguro ku matungo yabo ndetse na bo ubwabo? Ese ntibabona"
  32,28,"Baranavuga bati \"Ese uko kudukiranura kuzaba ryari, niba muri abanyakuri"
  32,29,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Ku munsi w’urubanza, ukwemera kwa babandi bahakanye ntacyo kuzabamarira kandi ntibazarindirizwa (kugira ngo bicuze)"
  32,30,"Bityo, birengagize unategereze (ibizababaho), mu by’ukuri, na bo bategereje (ibizakubaho)"